entries.s_800: Hey, are you the person that is supposed to take me to talk to Allard?
entries.s_802: Yes, I am supposed to take you.
entries.s_804: Well, I'm sorry to do this, but there has been a change of plan.  The information that I have is very time sensitive and this bum leg of mine will only slow you down.  You need to get to Allard within 20 minutes and give him this message: Wookiees walk at night in the trees of Naboo.
entries.s_806: Wookiees walk at night in the trees of Naboo?  What kind of code is that?
entries.s_808: It's one that one that will get us both killed if you don't hurry.  Go now!
entries.s_810: Got it.  I'm on my way.
entries.s_814: Why are you standing around, get moving!
entries.s_816: Can't a person just enjoy a lovely day?  Please leave me be.
